Rewrapped - Season 1, Episode 7




That Makes Two of Utz

In the Recreate Challenge contestants must remake the Utz Pretzel Rod from scratch: Will their creations turn from bread to dread or will their dough rise to the occasion? Then in the Innovate Challenge, will one contestant's original dish become a lightning rod for the judges' criticisms? Fun always strikes the same place twice on Rewrapped!




Original Air Date: 26-May-2014
